view` in sprint-state.json despite proof docs existing and 8 previous sessions fixing this.\n    36→- Epic-16 at `backlog` in sprint-status.yaml despite `done` in sprint-state.json epics section.\n    37→- sprint-state.json `sprint.done` was 70, should be 74.\n    38→- Fixed: set all 4 stories to `done`, epic-16 to `done`, sprint.done to 74 in both files.\n    39→- Root cause: ralph state reconciliation keeps overwriting story statuses. 9th occurrence today. This is a bug in the reconciliation logic that needs to be fixed as a priority.\n    40→\n    41→## Token Report\n    42→- Total tool calls: ~12\n    43→- By tool: Read: 5, Edit: 6, Grep: 2, Glob: 1\n    44→- Files read: 4 unique, 5 total reads\n    45→- Redundant operations: Entire session is redundant — same state corruption fix applied for the 9th time\n    46→\n    47→### Session 16 — state corruption fix #8 (2026-03-27T14:38Z)\n    48→\n    49→- Stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 AGAIN at `review` in sprint-state.json despite proof docs existing and previous 7 sessions fixing this.\n    50→- Epic-16 at `backlog` in sprint-status.yaml despite `done` in sprint-state.json epics section.\n    51→- sprint-state.json `sprint.done` was 70, should be 74.\n    52→- Fixed: set all 4 stories to `done`, epic-16 to `done`, sprint.done to 74 in both files.\n    53→- Root cause persists: ralph state reconciliation keeps overwriting story statuses. This is the 8th occurrence today.\n    54→\n    55→## Token Report\n    56→- Total tool calls: ~12\n    57→- By tool: Read: 4, Edit: 5, Grep: 3, Glob: 1\n    58→- Files read: 4 unique, 4 total reads\n    59→- Redundant operations: Entire session is redundant — same state corruption fix applied for the 8th time\n    60→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01DmuNz83ULVsePFUiguL8zC","session_id":"c6f68e62-2fdf-468a-8975-658f14ffd5c5","uuid":"c1b90c62-57f2-40a1-aee0-6970c976f148","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:48:29.530Z"}
